      "content": "hey im working on this python script that reads a massive csv file with pandas and it keeps hitting a MemoryError halfway through. i think im doing something wrong with how i handle the rows. is it better to use a list comprehension to store things or should i be using a generator? i need to keep the memory footprint low otherwise the whole thing just crashes.",
