      "content": "ok so i tried the chunksize thing but im still seeing some weird spikes in memory usage that i cant explain. it feels like even when i move to the next chunk, the memory doesnt fully drop back down and just keeps creeping up throughout the script. why would it do that? is there like a leak happening or something?",
